version_description: This tab is mostly based on Corey's Warner acoustic performance, published on the Youtube-channel The Rock Reel (https://youtu.be/mH19wwuL6cM). Notice that during the first verse he only plays root notes instead of complete chords.
I've determined that Corey Taylor uses a B5/G in the third measure of verses based on observations from this [video]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mH19wwuL6cM).
1st version of st marie in chords.
This are the simplified chords for this song in half step down tuning.
Acoustic you tube link to tab :https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jXkI1sTDoEg.
Version with Capo is easier to be played
